  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Burundi Relief Fund for COVID-19</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In this modern world, no country is able to escape and remains spared from events such as the COVID-19 pandemic. The country like Burundi, whose medical services and socio-economic life are inadequate, underfunded and too often inaccessible, is unable to have the medical equipment necessary to control and resist COVID-19. this fund will be used to purchase face masks, medical protective gear and COVID-19 test kits for its nurses and primary care physicians for immediate and long-term delivery.</narrative>
  </description>
